The following issue went on sale today:  Issuer:       Berkshire Hathaway Inc (BRK/A) 
Manager(s):  Bank of America Merrill Lynch  Goldman Sachs & Co
Amount:      $600 million
Coupon:      3.4 percent
Maturity:    Jan. 31, 2022
Settlement:  Jan. 31, 2012
Spread:      137.5 basis points more than governments
 